38:37.987 --> 38:40.120
It's just he lied about that.

38:44.585 --> 38:46.311
Joanna...

38:48.463 --> 38:51.431
[SOFT MUSIC]

38:52.126 --> 38:55.161
♪ ♪

39:08.650 --> 39:11.585
