39:59.724 --> 40:00.899
That's ridiculous.

40:00.924 --> 40:02.499
So you're telling me it isn't true?

40:02.524 --> 40:03.727
It's a vicious rumour.

40:04.766 --> 40:06.241
And you've been working way too hard,

40:06.265 --> 40:07.599
and if you weren't so
consumed by this case,

40:07.623 --> 40:08.949
you'd know better.

40:10.511 --> 40:11.797
Yeah?

40:12.704 --> 40:14.079
Of course.

40:14.214 --> 40:16.315
Honey, it's ludicrous.

40:17.860 --> 40:19.860
Surely you see that.

40:26.161 --> 40:27.781
Why would she lie to me?

40:27.876 --> 40:30.773
