for a quick payday.

40:31.093 --> 40:34.000
Gerrilyn Spence is a liar. She's crazy.

40:35.745 --> 40:37.126
"Crazy."

40:39.928 --> 40:41.828
Crazy like Mom was crazy?

40:45.359 --> 40:47.126
Hey...

40:47.795 --> 40:49.216
Sweetheart.

40:49.957 --> 40:52.423
Hey. I want you to come home with me.

40:52.754 --> 40:54.898
Right now. Come on.

40:55.696 --> 40:57.496
Come home with me.

40:58.995 --> 41:00.424
I can't.

41:00.970 --> 41:02.262
Yes, you can.

41:03.272 --> 41:04.865
No, I can't.

41:07.301 --> 41:08.765
I resign.

41:15.210 --> 41:17.143
[SOFT MUSIC]

41:17.212 --> 41:20.914
